to punish you himself.

500
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,900
- Let’s go.
- No, Ling Long!

501
00:36:59,901 --> 00:37:02,141
I don’t want to be punished!

502
00:37:02,142 --> 00:37:03,759
No!

503
00:37:04,797 --> 00:37:08,325
