508
00:37:26,920 --> 00:37:28,510
Brother Wu Tong!

509
00:37:29,480 --> 00:37:30,930
Brother Wu Tong!

510
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:32,759
What is it, Ling Long?

511
00:37:32,760 --> 00:37:36,525
